---
title  : LongJohns
summary: Documentation format stylized after ruby-lang.org

authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer
  - John Long

description:
  LongJohns (formerly LongFish) is a Ruby documentation template modeled after
  John Long's design of the offical Ruby website (http://ruby-lang.org).
  It allows any Ruby application or library to have a very Ruby-site look
  and feel.

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/longjohns
  code: http://github.com/rubyworks/longjohns

requires:
  - clap
  - rdazzle
  - syckle (build)

copyright: 
  Copyright 2009 Thomas Sawyer

